Package: coal.state
Type: Package
Title: 
    Classification, basis recalculation and conventional qualimetry of
    fossil solid fuels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yuri", "Possokhov", email = "possokhoff@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Coal-Coke", "", email = "info@coal-coke.com", role = "prn"))
Maintainer: Yuri Possokhov <possokhoff@gmail.com>
Description:
    The package provides functions for basis recalculations, unified 
    classification according to GOST 25543, and other routines conventional for
    chemical laboratories of coal-mining and coke-making industries.
